  <sys:String x:Key="FillAllConfirmTitle">Fill ALL stacks across every inventory?</sys:String>
  <sys:String x:Key="FillAllConfirmBody" xml:space="preserve">Fill _stackCount to max for {0} item(s) across {1} container(s) (every InventorySaveData block)?&#10;&#10;Items with max_stack_count &gt; 100 fill to max (capped at 9,999,999 — huge-cap items like currency stop there; stacks already larger are left alone).&#10;Items with max_stack_count ≤ 100 round up to the next full stack (e.g. count 120, max 50 → 150). Items already at a stack-boundary are skipped.&#10;&#10;Tip: the single-item "Fill stack" button fills to the true max, uncapped.&#10;&#10;Reversible by reloading the save without writing.</sys:String>
